{
  "stem": "471.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He took over the farm-- the-- the-- the-- the-- the factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When he came to Cracow, I don't want to get involve in that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I can just tell you only briefly, that [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bremer ?] deserve also-- but not maybe as-- maybe-- maybe he did more, well, maybe or less.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But Schindler was copying [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Bremer. ?] How he was copying the [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Bremer. ?] Because they were also going out from the ghetto to the factory, also going out from-- from-- from Plaszow to the factory, like we did.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But when we-- but [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Bremer ?] start to build barracks, he start to build barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He got the permission to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And eventually, they live on the premises there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But like I said before, he was a-- a-- a-- a top Nazi man, [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Bremer, ?] a pardoner, the real McCoy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He did-- he wasn't bad at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He didn't kill anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But he didn't do what-- what Schindler did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The bottom line is, OK, Schindler was a womanizer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everybody knew about.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Schindler was-- any-- anything, you name it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But the bottom line, he was thinking in advance, maybe I saved those thousand Jews, so I protect myself.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Maybe.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Maybe, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't-- I-- I-- I'm just presuming only.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So for that, he's-- what he got after the war, is coming to him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bottom line, he saved a thousand Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the way this happens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So here, where was the competition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were in competition?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were not in competition at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew each other.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you know, he was making-- he was making pots and pans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was making for the military, for the sub-- for-- for the marines.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were making.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, oh, later.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
